  <div class="intro" id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <h4>
    Arizona Bar Brokers was created with one purpose in mind, to be the best bar brokers in Arizona.  Our focus is 100% directed towards the bar business.  We set the standard and make the market for bar properties and bar brokerage transactions.  We bring buyers and sellers together to efficiently complete transactions.  Our goal is to facilitate transactions that are win-win for all parties involved.  Our team has over ten years of experience in the bar industry, including operations, business sales, and commercial real estate.
